{"tid":1948294,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[一再懷舊]卡巴拉島掛機私服 掛機就有點數(5)","createTime":"2020-03-29T02:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:01:24.000Z","uid":33821,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2445353a27c695b4fa074d4ce29a5bc63d35f81b","tid":1948294,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:08:28.000Z","msg":"主頁：<a href=\"http://www.icabala.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.icabala.com%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=d2ff5ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.icabala.com/</a><br />\nClient下載：<a href=\"http://www.icabala.com/thread-250-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.icabala.com%2Fthread-250-1-1.html&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=02341ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.icabala.com/thread-250-1-1.html</a><br />\n帳號註冊：<a href=\"http://reg.icabala.com/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Freg.icabala.com%2Findex.html&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=ae23dd8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://reg.icabala.com/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n由於舊有公會&quot;HKGOLDEN&quot;已經冇收新會員,所以新開咗公會叫&quot;HKLIHKG&quot;<br />\n歡迎到美加路廣場加入<br />\n<br />\n本Ser特色：<br />\n<br />\n1. 在線泡點就送點數，2分鐘1點，重新登錄即可查看到。<br />\n<br />\n2. 10倍基本經驗、10倍TM、3倍掉落率<br />\n<br />\n3. 天天打卡任務，遊戲中找到NPC小豬完成打卡任務每天獲得50點數，打卡累計30天獎勵1000點數<br />\n<br />\n4. 除10倍經驗基礎外，再加四倍經驗區：美加路森林-通往卡巴拉遺跡入口、美加路森林-通往白雪丘陵之路、白雪丘陵1-聖誕之境、塔吉吉火山4、塔巴斯克裡奧之城4層- 熔岩溫泉 (在上述地區打怪即有4倍經驗,衝等必去)<br />\n<br />\n5. 60級，120級送商城30天套裝加寵物，200級有機會得到永久披風<br />\n<br />\n6. 找NPC&ldquo;GM小豬&rdquo;完成卡等任務可以消除當前等級所有經驗 (維持等級,經驗值變0.0%, 刷BOSS必用)<br />\n<br />\n7. 去掉繁雜的99次、25次TM任務，只需要10次，即可得原來的10倍經驗 (草任TM經驗獎勵10倍)<br />\n<br />\n8. 商城加速飾品最低加速70%，最高150%，按等級遞增<br />\n<br />\n9. 完成劇情任務0-3，一共贈送90張倉庫券<br />\n<br />\n10. 設有混沌之塔(截至9/9，更新至61樓，傳點更新至61樓，可接60樓BOSS任)<br />\n<br />\n11. 點數支票：一種可以交易的點數，商城購買後可交易，賣給公會管理員安德魯就會得到相應點數 (100點支票每張市價約350萬，打幣賺點不是夢)<br />\n<br />\n12. 設有真正冒險家任務，400級並完成EP所有任務(EP0~EP6)可獲得終極發光裝備<br />\n<br />\n13. 新設地獄一、二層所有地圖及新BOSS科猶斯(須完成&ldquo;新開發室的傳聞&rdquo;系列任務（地獄前置任務320Lv～）) New!!<br />\n<br />\n舊post:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/17156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/17156</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/261340/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/261340/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/282134/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/282134/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/297047/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/297047/</a><br />\n<br />\n﹎﹎﹎﹎遊戲資料﹎﹎﹎﹎<br />\n請參考此文件：<a href=\"http://ppt.cc/mOn7d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fppt.cc%2FmOn7d&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=6f07985c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ppt.cc/mOn7d</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://drive.google.com/file/d/0BwDW3KY8J5GOU25qUGl6UGtscVE/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0BwDW3KY8J5GOU25qUGl6UGtscVE%2Fview&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=128279d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://drive.google.com/file/d/0BwDW3KY8J5GOU25qUGl6UGtscVE/view</a><br />\n<br />\n2轉資料<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/Co.php?bsn=05637&amp;sn=434429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D05637%26sn%3D434429&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=857786a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/Co.php?bsn=05637&amp;sn=434429</a>"},{"pid":"2143333640bf5a562a53d81f68edc4fa162932cf","tid":1948294,"uid":20174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:50:10.000Z","msg":"boost 推"},{"pid":"c71fa0f8ec735d690819ee3c3310fca1a21b2270","tid":1948294,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202